OOC: I believe the phrase for that is ooops...  sorry misread.  Anyway 
replace face with nose and it works out the same.

::Cygnar::
       He gasps and collapses on his back.  He clutches his head.  He sits up 
and shakes his head trying to refocus his thoughts.  He begins to think at 
her again with no real idea as to whether or not she'd even notice.  You must 
not do this now.  There will be time enough for it later.  For now, be who 
you once were.  He glances around desperately looking for something unknown.  
Please there is much that must be discussed first.

--part1_1a5.809f396.2aac1f69_boundary
